note: ian paulin is a songwriter/artists with a wealth of performing history touring major music events in Australia, UK and Europe, winning audiences with his combination fine story-telling in song and an alluring performing style. ian sings and writes with a rational passion. something really happens, you meet people, go places, yearn and learn through great songs and fine voice and skilful playing. ian is also an academic, community worker, and activist, presents ‘Deep-End’ Philosophy in the pub.
